<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.9.7">
<l>veṇṇeytā ṉamutu ceyya vekuṇṭumat tāycci yōcci</l>
<l>kaṇṇiyār kuṟuṅka yiṟṟāl kaṭṭaveṭ ṭeṉṟi runtāṉ</l>
<l>tiṇṇamā matiḷkaḷ cūḻnta teṉtirup pēruḷ vēlai</l>
<l>vaṇṇaṉār nāmam nāḷum vāymoḻin tuynta vāṟē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The way I was saved was by daily invoking the name of the one</l>
<l rend="indent">who sat fuming,</l>
<l>When the enraged herdess, wielding a [churning] rod, tied him</l>
<l>With a small, knot-filled rope since he gobbled up the ghee,</l>
<l>The sea-hued one in Tiruppēr of the South, encircled by strong, great walls,</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
